<br>
Find a nice large guild on your server, or a few, speak with the raid leader(s) and see if you can tag along when they go after CT.<br>
<br>
You go in there Solo, you're looking at hours of CR (trying to get a friend to get it or even worse, your stuck getting it).<br>
<br>
Fear's easy to get around, but if you don't know the zone first hand, there is no way you will survive it, I'm sorry... <p><p align=center>
